snippet.title: Six Hours at Hugo's Update 2.0 Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the game here: https://gamejolt.com/games/six-hours-at-hugos/739024

This update aims to improve upon the previous version of Six Hours at Hugo's, and make it a more enjoyable and memorable experience overall. This update will feature some quality of life improvements, as well as some more game changing features such as:

Challenges,
Free Roam,
Customization,
A Model Viewer,
Achievements,
and more!

Check out the game page on GameJolt for more information on the update.
